==English==
'''quinella'''
===Noun===
# a form of [[bet]], where the better must pick the first two finishers in a race, without concern for the order of finishing.

===Verb===
{{rfv-sense}}
# Verb usage of the noun '''quinella'''
#: ''Australia quinella'd in the 400m, with Thorpe narrowly beating Hackett.''

